ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#54: FILE: mm/shmem.c:768:
+	if ((offset = shmem_clear_swp (entry,info->i_direct, SHMEM_NR_DIRECT)) >= 0)

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

